3
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:45,020
[Episode 12]

4
00:01:46,509 --> 00:01:49,610
[Lake Pavilion, Nanzhou]

5
00:01:50,090 --> 00:01:50,580
Come.

6
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,100
Please.

7
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:53,979
What an achievement.

8
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:56,420
Congratulations.

9
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:04,460
It's so lively.

10
00:02:04,860 --> 00:02:07,780
It seems that the host of the banquet

11
00:02:07,810 --> 00:02:09,340
is a big name in Nanzhou.

12
00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:10,949
He indeed is.

13
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,680
You're his servant?

14
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:14,810
Yes.

15
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:18,140
He was born a master.

16
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,530
I was born a servant.

17
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:22,240
Both of his sons

18
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,590
passed the exam to become the Imperial Scholars.

19
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:24,890
I...

20
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:27,820
I'm happy for him.

21
00:02:31,730 --> 00:02:32,350
Sir,

22
00:02:33,329 --> 00:02:34,310
are you drunk?

23
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:36,880
So what?

24
00:02:37,050 --> 00:02:38,320
I'm still rowing the boat

25
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:39,220
as steadily as ever.

26
00:02:39,490 --> 00:02:40,410
After ferrying you,

27
00:02:40,850 --> 00:02:42,450
I'm going to pick up

28
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:44,410
his two sons.

29
00:02:44,490 --> 00:02:45,850
The distinguished guests are here.

30
00:02:46,250 --> 00:02:48,170
Please.

31
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,550
Prefectural Governor Xiong, Administrator Luo.

32
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:52,100
Commander Su,

33
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:55,470
although Master Xie is not one of Nanzhou Four Scholars,

34
00:02:55,890 --> 00:02:56,910
he is the most renowned

35
00:02:57,170 --> 00:02:58,990
in this city.

36
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,050
His two sons

37
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,890
are both qualified as Imperial Scholars,

38
00:03:02,050 --> 00:03:03,000
which brings great honor

39
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,990
to the entire Nanzhou.

40
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:06,770
Congratulations.

41
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:08,570
Thank you.

42
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:10,060
Master Xie,

43
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:13,800
Commander Su is very capable in the capital.

44
00:03:14,890 --> 00:03:16,510
His sworn sister

45
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:19,350
is the daughter of Assistant Minister Pei of the Ministry of Personnel Administration.

46
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,920
Commander Su,

47
00:03:22,270 --> 00:03:22,940
Miss Pei.

48
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:27,130
Please take care of my sons in the future.

49
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:29,400
One of them is named Xie Ming,

50
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,900
the other one is Xie Hui.

51
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:32,780
Commander Su,

52
00:03:33,170 --> 00:03:33,610
please.

53
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:34,220
Let's go in.

54
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:41,310
Minister Lu.

55
00:03:42,970 --> 00:03:43,620
Headman Xie.

56
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,180
What are you doing here?

57
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:47,010
Master Xie is my uncle.

58
00:03:48,980 --> 00:03:49,760
Your surname is Xie too.

59
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:50,660
Please.

60
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:51,340
Please.

61
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:53,190
The two young masters are here!

62
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:54,800
They're here.

63
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:55,850
They are amazing.

64
00:03:55,890 --> 00:03:58,010
They are very fortunate.

65
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,740
Yeah.

66
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:01,780
They're coming this way.

67
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,920
The two on the boat are my sons.

68
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,430
It's so enviable.

69
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,320
Those two young men look like…

70
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:38,350
Help!

71
00:04:38,490 --> 00:04:39,890
Help them!

72
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:41,940
Somebody help!

73
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:43,920
Help!

74
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:45,360
Help!

75
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:47,409
Help me!

76
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:50,080
Help!

77
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:52,560
Please help!

78
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,760
Ming.

79
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,840
Hui.

80
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,670
How can I live

81
00:05:33,150 --> 00:05:36,110
without both of you?

82
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:45,270
The murderer ferried us here.

83
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:46,780
He claimed to be the servant

84
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:48,460
of this family, didn't he?

85
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,840
He is my uncle's old servant.

86
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,180
It turns out that he never got over what happened back then.

87
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,050
How could he do this?

88
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,150
Shut up!

89
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:57,480
Uncle.

90
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,180
Xie.

91
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,160
Do you know why you‘re here?

92
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:17,040
Yes.

93
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:18,500
Then cut to the chase.

94
00:06:19,130 --> 00:06:21,290
That old servant and Master Xie were on bad terms?

95
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:22,390
Tell me the details.

96
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,560
Uncle is nice to me,

97
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:26,750
I'm not supposed

98
00:06:26,930 --> 00:06:28,280
to speak ill of him.

99
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,600
But he was indeed at fault

100
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,670
in that incident.

101
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:35,960
That old servant's son

102
00:06:36,659 --> 00:06:38,300
was the same age as Xie Ming and Xie Hui.

103
00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:39,490
Therefore,

104
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,659
he'd been serving them since very young.

105
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:42,850
That day

106
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:44,690
was the birthday of my two cousins.

107
00:06:44,890 --> 00:06:46,040
They insisted on going for a boat ride on the lake,

108
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,320
and my uncle agreed.

109
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:49,820
It was sunny at first,

110
00:06:50,170 --> 00:06:52,010
but the sky clouded up suddenly.

111
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,220
Hold on tight!

112
00:06:59,380 --> 00:06:59,940
Dad!

113
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:01,250
Hold on to something!

114
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:02,580
Watch out!

115
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:04,980
Hold on tight!

116
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,380
Xie Ming!

117
00:07:06,810 --> 00:07:07,530
Hold on tight!

118
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:08,310
Young Master!

119
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,190
Xie Ming!

120
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:10,050
-Young Master! -Xie Ming!

121
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:10,750
Young Master!

122
00:07:10,890 --> 00:07:11,630
Xie Ming.

123
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,190
-What should we do now?  -Xie Ming.

124
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:13,910
Young Master!

125
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,390
-Save him! -Young Master!

126
00:07:15,710 --> 00:07:17,830
Go save him, can you?

127
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:18,940
Save him!

128
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,470
Go save him!

129
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:22,150
Son!

130
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,340
Xie Ming!

131
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:24,210
Be careful, son!

132
00:07:24,590 --> 00:07:25,030
Watch out!

133
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:26,010
Come back!

134
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:27,170
-Xie Ming! -Hurry up!

135
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,290
Hurry up!

136
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:29,280
Come on!

137
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,470
Hurry up, son!

138
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:31,290
Hurry up!

139
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:33,540
Young Master, are you alright?

140
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:35,270
Son, swim back now!

141
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:36,370
-My son is fine. -Son!

142
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,520
My son is fine.

143
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,000
The storm is too strong.

144
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:40,880
Go back to the shore!

145
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,350
Son, swim back now!

146
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:43,220
Master,

147
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,630
my son is still in the water!

148
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:45,590
We can't leave now!

149
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:47,100
Hurry, go back to the shore!

150
00:07:47,210 --> 00:07:48,170
The raging storm

151
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,680
may upset the boat any second!

152
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,460
Son!

153
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,790
It was very windy on the lake that time.

154
00:07:55,550 --> 00:07:56,550
They had to go back to the shore immediately

155
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,080
or the boat might be knocked over.

156
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:00,620
But…

157
00:08:01,130 --> 00:08:02,600
My uncle decision

158
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,520
was indeed kind of selfish.

159
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:07,750
That old servant's son

160
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:09,950
drowned?

161
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,900
Yeah.

162
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,560
That old servant nearly drowned too.

163
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:13,870
He was lucky.

164
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,060
He was sent to the shore by the waves.

165
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:16,310
His son's body was not found

166
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:17,660
until three days later.

167
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,740
That old servant was quite a character.

168
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,940
After his son died,

169
00:08:22,150 --> 00:08:23,430
he didn't seek revenge immediately.

170
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:26,880
He waited for more than ten years

171
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,730
to get back at

172
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,180
the Xie brothers

173
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:31,750
when they are qualified as Imperial Scholars.

174
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,440
It's too cruel.

175
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:39,659
Headman Xie,

176
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:41,000
I want to ask you something.

177
00:08:41,299 --> 00:08:42,610
Are Xie Ming and Xie Hui

178
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:44,570
in the painting of the Stone Bridge?

179
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:45,770
What?

180
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,590
The painting of the Stone Bridge?

181
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:51,500
Looks like he doesn't know about this.

182
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:52,530
Xijun,

183
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:54,520
have you found something?

184
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:56,960
The painting was drawn

185
00:08:56,990 --> 00:08:58,380
by Zhang Xuan 15 years ago.

186
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:00,570
The two kids playing chess in the painting

187
00:09:00,810 --> 00:09:01,360
should be

188
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:02,550
the Xie brothers.

189
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:03,530
Besides,

190
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,590
even though the servant in the painting has his back to the viewers,

191
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:07,140
but judging from his shape,

192
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,360
he should be the old servant tonight.

193
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:12,020
The two kids playing chess in the painting

194
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,190
are Xie Ming and Xie Hui?

195
00:09:13,490 --> 00:09:15,210
Miss Pei, do you have any proof?

196
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:16,410
Don't make

197
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,950
wild guesses at such a serious case.

198
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,240
It's not a wild guess.

199
00:09:21,310 --> 00:09:22,080
It's just that

200
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,900
Zhang Xuan was so good as a painter.

201
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:24,920
He managed to

202
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:25,920
portray the traits of the figures in the painting.

203
00:09:26,410 --> 00:09:27,780
So, although the brothers had grown up,

204
00:09:28,070 --> 00:09:29,640
it's not hard to recognize them.

205
00:09:30,210 --> 00:09:31,370
When I laid my eyes on the two Imperial Scholars

206
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,150
on the island today,

207
00:09:33,490 --> 00:09:34,890
I found them familiar immediately.

208
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:37,250
Later, when I looked at their bodies close,

209
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:39,020
I knew I was right.

210
00:09:40,140 --> 00:09:42,980
If Xijun was right,

211
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:47,420
Nanzhou Four Scholars

212
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:50,130
are not the only people who died and would die.

213
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:53,970
Everyone

214
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:56,720
in the painting of the Stone Bridge is doomed.

215
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:01,980
Su Wuming,

216
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:03,540
stop making unsupported speculations

217
00:10:03,570 --> 00:10:04,290
with your sworn sister.

218
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:06,380
No matter what,

219
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,340
tomorrow morning,

220
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:11,000
I'll go meet Master Xie in person.

221
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,220
Miss Pei,

222
00:10:14,850 --> 00:10:16,200
I know you're good at painting,

223
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:17,900
but I don't believe

224
00:10:17,930 --> 00:10:18,850
you're that observant.

225
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:20,060
If you are wrong,

226
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:22,140
please don't meddle in

227
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:23,390
our investigations again.

228
00:10:24,170 --> 00:10:25,370
But if what you said

229
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,210
is proven right,

230
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:28,590
that'll be the key to crack this case.

231
00:10:29,290 --> 00:10:31,570
I'll owe you a deep debt of gratitude.

232
00:10:35,970 --> 00:10:37,070
Master Xie, I'm sorry for your loss.

233
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:39,920
Sir,

234
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:43,170
your two sons just passed away.

235
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,140
I shouldn't have disturb you at this time,

236
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,800
but it's my duty

237
00:10:46,830 --> 00:10:48,610
to look into criminal cases.

238
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:49,970
I have to

239
00:10:50,970 --> 00:10:52,370
ask you some questions.

240
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,680
My grief now

241
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,880
is already beyond measure,

242
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:03,320
things can't get any worse.

243
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,500
Whatever you want to ask me about,

244
00:11:05,810 --> 00:11:07,420
just go ahead.

245
00:11:07,810 --> 00:11:09,730
Are the two kids

246
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:10,880
in the painting of the Stone Bridge

247
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,590
your two sons?

248
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:21,740
Yes.

249
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,810
They are Xie Ming and Xie Hui.

250
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,330
I'm all ears.

251
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:39,960
Back then,

252
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:44,040
when Zhang Xuan travelled to Nanzhou,

253
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:45,860
he was down and out.

254
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:48,410
He stayed at my house.

255
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:51,950
It was my two sons who took him

256
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:54,370
to the Nanzhou Four Scholars.

257
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,910
Is the man facing backwards

258
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,120
the old servant

259
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:03,020
who murdered your sons that day?

260
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:07,110
Yes.

261
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:08,980
His son

262
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:10,810
drowned

263
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,160
in an attempt for saving my son.

264
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:14,500
I've been guilty since then.

265
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,810
I gave him a lot of money

266
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:19,710
and thought he had let it go.

267
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:22,660
I never imagined he would exact revenge

268
00:12:23,210 --> 00:12:25,080
after all these years.

269
00:12:26,890 --> 00:12:30,140
My poor sons!

270
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,400
I know what you're thinking.

271
00:12:48,430 --> 00:12:49,230
I'm a man of my word.

272
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:50,500
I don't need you to remind me.

273
00:13:09,850 --> 00:13:11,580
I borrowed the painting of the Stone Bridge again.

274
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:13,070
Let's take a close look at it.

275
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:18,730
This painting is evil.

276
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:20,980
It was nice

277
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:21,990
to live in Nanzhou

278
00:13:22,210 --> 00:13:23,570
until all of a sudden,

279
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:25,590
this case became even creepier

280
00:13:25,620 --> 00:13:26,770
than the Chang'an black tea case.

281
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,620
I've drank too much yesterday,

282
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:30,490
the hangover is killing me.

283
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:31,750
I'll leave the scrutinize of the painting to you.

284
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:34,140
There's someone hidden here.

285
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:35,680
Where?

286
00:13:36,180 --> 00:13:36,770
Where?

287
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,670
On the branch.

288
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:43,960
There's a woodcutter lying between the branches.

289
00:13:44,450 --> 00:13:45,620
His face is blurry,

290
00:13:46,170 --> 00:13:47,430
but given his shape,

291
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,300
he was a young man when the painting was drawn.

292
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:52,740
He should be in his mid thirties now.

293
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:56,530
Lu Lingfeng,

294
00:13:57,250 --> 00:13:58,940
now that you're not the acting minister anymore,

295
00:13:59,340 --> 00:14:01,170
but Headman Xie and Headman Huang…

296
00:14:01,190 --> 00:14:02,140
They're still at my service.

297
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:03,080
Leave it to me.

298
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,790
Who on earth is the one

299
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:11,770
intending to kill everyone in this painting?

300
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:14,150
I think we should

301
00:14:14,180 --> 00:14:15,130
stay away from it.

302
00:14:15,890 --> 00:14:17,570
Maybe this painting

303
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:19,270
was cursed by someone powerful.

304
00:14:19,770 --> 00:14:21,050
