307
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,650
The first victim,

308
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:34,550
Yan Yuanfu.

309
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,600
You mean,

310
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:41,580
Yan Yuanfu came back as a ghost and

311
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:42,910
killed those people?

312
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:45,650
In this world,

313
00:14:46,410 --> 00:14:48,710
there are neither gods nor ghosts.

314
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:52,280
They are just

315
00:14:53,570 --> 00:14:54,140
humans in disguise.

316
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:00,800
Here we are.

317
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:03,970
Mr. Ma.

318
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,130
Mr. Ma.

319
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:07,440
Where is he?

320
00:15:08,970 --> 00:15:10,430
He must have gone to collect firewood.

321
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,140
Are you sure the owner of this hut

322
00:15:12,390 --> 00:15:13,960
is the woodcutter in the painting?

323
00:15:14,230 --> 00:15:14,910
Yeah.

324
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,560
He's been bragging about appearing

325
00:15:16,930 --> 00:15:17,890
in that painting all the time.

326
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:18,570
He also said

327
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:20,530
it's a pity that his face isn't clearly shown.

328
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,250
Great.

329
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:24,340
We've done a great job this time.

330
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:51,250
Mr. Ma,

331
00:15:51,710 --> 00:15:52,860
these officers are here for you.

332
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,170
You're so lucky

333
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:54,910
to be in that painting.

334
00:15:55,090 --> 00:15:56,330
They are bring you back to

335
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,050
let you live in comfort.

336
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:00,240
Damn.

337
00:16:24,090 --> 00:16:25,100
Sorry, Commander Su.

338
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:26,640
We were too late.

339
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,330
That cliff is too high.

340
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,490
To find the body,

341
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:30,390
it will take at least three to five days,

342
00:16:30,410 --> 00:16:31,170
half a month at most.

343
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:32,930
Besides, there are many beasts in that mountain.

344
00:16:32,990 --> 00:16:33,510
I'm afraid...

345
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:36,710
Lu Lingfeng,

346
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,850
we need to visit the prefectural governor.

347
00:16:40,710 --> 00:16:41,200
I know

348
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:42,400
you think that Yan Yuanfu's death is suspicious,

349
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:44,300
but he was already buried days ago.

350
00:16:49,070 --> 00:16:49,700
That's why

351
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,660
we must get

352
