the approval of Prefectural Governor Xiong.

353
00:16:54,290 --> 00:16:55,160
What?

354
00:16:56,350 --> 00:16:58,540
You want to dig Yan Yuanfu out?

355
00:16:59,120 --> 00:16:59,750
Yes.

356
00:16:59,930 --> 00:17:01,220
You can't find the murderer,

357
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:02,300
and think identifying Yan Yuanfu

358
00:17:02,330 --> 00:17:03,470
