361
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:07,609
Therefore,

362
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:10,819
I suspect that Yan Yuanfu was murdered too.

363
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,390
Commander Su,

364
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:13,819
Yan Yuanfu

365
00:17:13,849 --> 00:17:15,380
was buried days ago.

366
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:16,869
If I allow you to dig his grave,

367
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,520
how am I going to

368
