375
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:32,750
and have no idea

376
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:33,740
where to find the next clue.

377
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,090
So you think

378
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:36,210
you can find something from

379
00:17:36,250 --> 00:17:36,780
Yan Yuanfu's body?

380
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:40,050
Yeah. You can say that.

381
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,170
Not all murderers

382
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:43,520
can be brought to justice.

383
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:45,830
Even your teacher Detective Di

384
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:47,880
who have solved countless mysterious cases in his life,

385
00:17:48,330 --> 00:17:49,250
couldn't say

386
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:51,750
that he had no regrets at all!

387
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:53,220
Detective Di taught me

388
00:17:54,060 --> 00:17:55,700
