396
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:14,270
I'm not.

397
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:15,890
On the contrary,

398
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:18,200
I was expelled from the capital

399
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:20,730
because I offended Her Highness.

400
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:23,210
Anyway, that has nothing to do

401
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,850
with what we're talking about now.

402
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:27,190
The number of victims keeps increasing

403
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:29,020
and the murderer is still at large.

404
00:18:29,150 --> 00:18:32,070
As an official, I should

405
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:34,300
catch the murderer as soon as possible

406
00:18:34,490 --> 00:18:36,350
and bring peace back to Nanzhou.

407
00:18:37,540 --> 00:18:38,700
That's eloquent.

408
00:18:43,010 --> 00:18:45,180
What if I don't agree?

409
00:18:48,050 --> 00:18:49,520
You should be worth your salt.

410
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:52,070
If you can't do that, you're a coward

411
00:18:52,770 --> 00:18:53,540
who fails in your duty.

412
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,210
I didn't ask for your opinion!

413
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,180
You must have heard

414
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:01,580
that I've been dismissed from my post

415
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:02,580
