416
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:03,760
However, I studied and practiced martial arts

417
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,990
with His Highness from a young age.

418
00:19:06,550 --> 00:19:07,550
No one in the Eastern Palace

419
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,450
