420
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,240
the way you did.

421
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:19,210
I've sent my disciple, Xue Huan

422
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:21,690
to the capital

423
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:22,750
to report the strange deaths in Nanzhou

424
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:24,230
to His Highness.

425
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:26,870
Prefectural Governor Xiong,

426
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:28,850
make a wise decision.

427
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:30,400
You...

428
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,060
Don't.

429
00:19:38,890 --> 00:19:40,960
When did you send Xue Huan back to the capital?

430
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:42,820
I didn't.

431
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:44,690
He's just a kid and it's a long way.

432
00:19:44,860 --> 00:19:45,740
I'd be worried sick.

433
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:47,740
You lied to them?

434
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,090
Well done!

435
00:19:53,730 --> 00:19:54,340
Why are you laughing?

436
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:57,230
I've been suspecting

437
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:58,540
that you and His Highness

438
00:19:58,560 --> 00:20:00,090
have some secret plan.

439
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:01,950
Do you?

440
00:20:02,610 --> 00:20:03,340
Of course not.

441
00:20:03,650 --> 00:20:05,140
But you were so convincing

442
00:20:05,250 --> 00:20:06,560
when you lied back there.

443
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:07,650
I learned it from you.

444
00:20:08,650 --> 00:20:09,010
No,

445
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,620
I learned it from Chicken Fed.

446
00:20:12,860 --> 00:20:13,940
That odd man's trick

447
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,220
is quite effective

448
00:20:17,930 --> 00:20:19,160
in dealing with someone like Prefectural Governor Xiong.

449
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:21,750
Lu Lingfeng,

450
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:23,000
you've changed.

451
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:24,710
You're no longer

452
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:25,860
that frank and impulsive young man

453
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,940
when we first met.

454
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:27,840
Today, if you…

455
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,800
That's not important.

456
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,060
You should think about

457
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,120
the autopsy tomorrow.

458
00:20:33,870 --> 00:20:35,890
You're right, General.

459
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:44,820
[Notice]

460
00:20:56,750 --> 00:21:00,190
My poor son!

461
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:05,980
You don't deserve to be treated like this.

462
00:21:07,150 --> 00:21:09,030
My poor son!

463
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:13,580
Prefectural Governor,

464
00:21:17,290 --> 00:21:20,130
are you really going to let them open the coffin?

465
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:26,920
Madam,

466
00:21:27,950 --> 00:21:30,070
your son was my old friend.

467
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:32,840
If I fail to find a clue after opening the coffin,

468
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:35,410
I'll do everything to make it up

469
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,760
to him when I meet him

470
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:39,440
in the underworld.

471
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:41,020
What's the use of saying this?

472
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:42,630
Yeah.

473
00:21:43,020 --> 00:21:44,460
The weather is cold now,

474
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:48,160
how can you expose my son's body to the biting wind?

475
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,580
I'm his mother,

476
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:53,180
but I can't stop you from doing that on him!

477
00:21:53,970 --> 00:21:55,910
I'm not worth living!

478
00:21:58,230 --> 00:21:58,890
Commander Su,

479
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:00,020
it's time.

480
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,190
My poor son!

481
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:06,640
Open the coffin.

482
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:07,610
Yes.

483
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:09,780
My son!

484
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:10,630
Mom.

485
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:11,590
Madam.

486
00:22:11,660 --> 00:22:12,370
Mother.

487
00:22:15,270 --> 00:22:17,140
-Mother. -My poor son!

488
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,990
My poor son!

489
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:26,330
Mom! Mom!

490
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,060
Mom!

491
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:29,520
Su Wuming!

492
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:30,800
You'll pay for this!

493
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:32,570
Mom.

494
00:23:17,170 --> 00:23:18,140
Look at this.

495
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,780
What's the problem?

496
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:27,660
Is there any problem?

497
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:28,540
What has happened actually?

498
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:29,900
It's been so long.

499
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:35,750
Rain cover!

500
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:54,190
Mom!

501
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,350
Mom!

502
00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:00,620
It's raining.

503
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:05,220
Even God can't stand it!

504
00:24:07,420 --> 00:24:09,180
-God! -Prefectural Governor,

505
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:10,730
it's raining heavily. Let's take shelter from the rain.

506
00:24:11,690 --> 00:24:12,200
Prefectural Governor,

507
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,700
my brother, Yuanfu, died of illness.

508
00:24:15,220 --> 00:24:16,900
But Su Wuming insisted on opening the coffin.

509
00:24:17,420 --> 00:24:19,330
They haven't found

510
00:24:19,370 --> 00:24:20,570
any trace till now.

511
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,390
Please punish him

512
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,750
to comfort the dead!

513
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:25,020
That's right!

514
00:24:25,430 --> 00:24:26,670
Punish him! Punish him!

515
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:27,650
Yes!

516
00:24:27,670 --> 00:24:29,310
Even God can't stand it!

517
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:31,410
Seal the coffin again

518
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:33,710
and let Mr. Yan rest in peace!

519
00:24:33,740 --> 00:24:35,220
Don't move!

520
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:36,540
Let Mr. Yan rest in peace!

521
00:24:36,570 --> 00:24:37,450
Don't move!

522
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,490
Back off! Back off!

523
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:40,010
Don't come any closer. Back off!

524
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:41,170
Back off!

525
00:24:41,850 --> 00:24:42,900
Back off!

526
00:24:43,740 --> 00:24:44,430
Stop it!

527
00:24:56,410 --> 00:24:57,490
I am Lu Lingfeng

528
00:24:58,060 --> 00:24:58,900
from the Lu family of Fanyang,

529
00:24:59,250 --> 00:25:01,360
the former General of the Imperial Guards.

530
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:04,220
There is an official notice from the government,

531
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:06,860
stating that Commander Su was ordered to examine the body.

532
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:10,930
Let's see who dares to stir up trouble!

533
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:18,150
Madam Yan,

534
00:25:18,780 --> 00:25:19,860
people of Nanzhou,

535
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:21,260
Commander Su

536
00:25:21,840 --> 00:25:23,500
was the disciple of Detective Di Renjie.

537
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,060
Several months ago,

538
00:25:25,330 --> 00:25:26,690
he solved the mysterious Chang'an black tea case,

539
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:27,920
overawing the government officials.

540
00:25:28,490 --> 00:25:30,060
Even His Highness,

541
00:25:30,230 --> 00:25:31,110
Her Highness,

542
00:25:31,410 --> 00:25:32,600
and His Majesty

543
00:25:32,860 --> 00:25:34,250
heaped praises on him.

544
00:25:34,620 --> 00:25:36,840
Recently in Nanzhou,

545
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:38,810
murder cases happened one after another.

546
00:25:40,020 --> 00:25:42,580
They are all related to the Nanzhou Four Scholars

547
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:44,110
and the painting of the Stone Bridge.

548
00:25:44,810 --> 00:25:45,820
The opening of the coffin today

549
00:25:46,210 --> 00:25:47,280
is reasonable

550
00:25:47,670 --> 00:25:48,800
and necessary

551
00:25:49,010 --> 00:25:49,800
to solve the cases.

552
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,000
Only the culprit

553
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:53,330
will act maliciously and try to stop it.

554
00:25:54,630 --> 00:25:56,760
Please think carefully about it.

555
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,290
Don't say I didn't warn you.

556
00:26:01,340 --> 00:26:02,100
That's right.

557
00:26:02,350 --> 00:26:03,950
What he said is all correct.

558
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:07,290
I totally agree with him.

559
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:37,610
I, Su Wuming, would like to thank you

560
00:26:38,930 --> 00:26:41,310
for defending me today.

561
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,330
If you hadn't been so brave

562
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:46,240
to dig the grave,

563
00:26:46,810 --> 00:26:47,370
I wouldn't have

564
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,240
said that.

565
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:49,920
Su Wuming,

566
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:53,260
have you ever thought

567
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:54,550
that you might lose your position

568
00:26:55,190 --> 00:26:56,400
because of this?

569
00:26:57,890 --> 00:26:58,410
Is it worth it?

570
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:03,170
It was not the Imperial Guards' duty

571
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:07,050
