574
00:27:10,450 --> 00:27:13,190
But you killed the Ghost Four,

575
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:15,010
and killed the real murderer, Yuan Lai.

576
00:27:15,050 --> 00:27:15,880
However,

577
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:18,360
you ended up like this.

578
00:27:18,690 --> 00:27:20,190
Have you ever thought

579
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:21,910
whether it was worth it?

580
00:27:25,630 --> 00:27:26,740
Even if I could go back in time,

581
00:27:27,940 --> 00:27:30,230
I would still be nosy.

582
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,680
My teacher Detective Di

583
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,350
was right.

